{"tid":2254022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BNO居留簽證無限額 明年1.31起接受申請 5年付2,540港元","createTime":"2020-10-22T14:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T10:58:13.000Z","uid":51620,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"07c37db1374f3d5bc14f4d65b8331353761067dd","tid":2254022,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"繼英國早前公佈放寬國民（海外）護照（BNO）持有人移民，英國當局再公佈，所有合資格申請BNO的香港人，可於明年1月31日起申請BNO居留簽證；而英國沒有對該等申請設限額，5年期簽證申請費用為每人250英鎊，折合約2,358港元。<br />\n<br />\n英國內政部護照署早前指，簡稱BNO的英國國民（海外）護照，截至今年7月中發行數字為374,806本，而今年首7個月續領獲批數字為58,335本，護照署亦指因疫情影響部門運作延誤審批程序，當中4月只有196本，當局已加快人手處理。當局亦確認未取得護照正本人士，若有需要可以申請緊急護照（ETD），可在英國政府網站申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/CQKOI5YLNBAVFJ4WTNJHYQFCEA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2FCQKOI5YLNBAVFJ4WTNJHYQFCEA%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=e23f6ab9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2FCQKOI5YLNBAVFJ4WTNJHYQFCEA%2F&h=97eb3520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/CQKOI5YLNBAVFJ4WTNJHYQFCEA/</a>"},{"pid":"e239dd491ae51feb4b8c63c4158c0a99c7a47c9f","tid":2254022,"uid":2054,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:03:19.000Z","msg":"2000萬變2500<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03af5a900f16f69e5b738889a0521cbdb99e34fe","tid":2254022,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e239dd491ae51feb4b8c63c4158c0a99c7a47c9f","tid":2254022,"uid":2054,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:03:19.000Z","msg":"2000萬變2500<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse